  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BEFORE YOU BUY: This is a short horror experience, a creepy hidden object game. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter Jessica's world, where she battles realistic hallucinations. Jessica faces creepy dreams that could end her life with one wrong move. Help her get back to reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/88856036dc8a812451939868859adff1.poster.avif?t=1763288340\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/88856036dc8a812451939868859adff1.webm?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/88856036dc8a812451939868859adff1.mp4?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In prologue round take a look around the room and remember how the objects are positioned and where they're scattered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/e0e127281c2a1029537c10fbca36e330.poster.avif?t=1763288340\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/e0e127281c2a1029537c10fbca36e330.webm?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/e0e127281c2a1029537c10fbca36e330.mp4?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to pass 7 times correctly to win.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Green exit => everything is as in prologue round</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Red exit => something is wrong</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/057e9d9b76452ee41dcf1e11ef1e62cd.poster.avif?t=1763288340\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/057e9d9b76452ee41dcf1e11ef1e62cd.webm?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/057e9d9b76452ee41dcf1e11ef1e62cd.mp4?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVELS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The Hall</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The Basement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The Hospital</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/81b6205ff2c127f7ab540bbb4fe518e1.poster.avif?t=1763288340\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/81b6205ff2c127f7ab540bbb4fe518e1.webm?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/81b6205ff2c127f7ab540bbb4fe518e1.mp4?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HAVE FUN!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >... and don't be scared! :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/06545b4459c5ea15c049ae267073ae0a.poster.avif?t=1763288340\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/06545b4459c5ea15c049ae267073ae0a.webm?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816410/extras/06545b4459c5ea15c049ae267073ae0a.mp4?t=1763288340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
